Cape Town - The body of Chanelle McCrawl, 10, was found the on the banks of the Vygieskraal River in Athlone Industria on Friday. Her mother Charmaine says Chanelle went to school on Thursday morning and she never arrived home, she went looking for her daughter. Her classmates says the little girl never arrived at school that day. Police say the girl was reported missing yesterday. Spokesperson, Noloyiso Rwexana, says they've opened a murder investigation. " A body of a 10-year-old girl was found this morning in Primrose Park in Manenberg." The gruesome discovery by her grandmother has outraged residents of Manenberg. She then alerted neighbours who contacted authorities. The circumstances surrounding her murder are under investigation.  To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
